Hazel Forbes https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hazel_Forbes 0 Hazel Forbes (born Hazel Froidevaux, November 26, 1910 – November 19, 1980) was an American dancer and actress from Gettysburg, South Dakota. She was blond and petite. Hazel_Forbes ( born Hazel_Froidevaux , November_26_,_1910 – November_19_,_1980 ) was an_American_dancer_and_actress from Gettysburg , South_Dakota . She was blond_and_petite .
